  # List Timeline Events
  
  âœ… **PUBLIC ENDPOINT**: No authentication required
  
  Returns all timeline events sorted by year (descending) and creation date.
  
  ## Response Format:
  ```json
  [
    {
      "id": "uuid",
      "year": "2023",
      "title": "Bachelor Degree",
      "description": "Completed Bachelor of Science in Computer Science",
      "type": "education",
      "location": "University of Technology",
      "image": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
      "createdAt": "2023-01-01T00:00:00.000Z"
    }
  ]
  ```
  
  ## Timeline Event Types:
  - `education` - Educational achievements
  - `achievement` - Personal achievements
  - `work` - Work experience
}